
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-websec-framework-reqs-00.txt'>
    <title>"Web Security Framework: Problem Statement and Requirements", Jeff Hodges</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-websec-framework-reqs-00.txt</link>
    <description>Web-based malware and attacks are proliferating rapidly on the Internet.  New web security mechanisms are also rapidly growing in number, although in an incoherent fashion.  This document provides a brief overview of the present situation and the various seemingly piece-wise approaches being taken to mitigate the threats.  It then provides an overview of requirements as presently being expressed by the community in various online and face-to-face discussions.</description>
    <dc:date>2013-02-17T23:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
